Package: bacenR
Title: Access Data from Brazilian Central Bank: Active Institutions, Balance Sheets and Normative Acts 
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Ricardo", "Theodoro", , "rtheodoro@usp.br", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6741-5153"))
Description: Provides functions to query, retrieve, and tidy economic and
    financial data from Brazilian Central Bank web services for use in R
    analyses and workflows. Active institutions information, balance sheets and normative acts.
License: GPL (>= 3)
